      "title": "Schools to reopen on 21st July",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Due to the fuel shortage in the country, school holidays have been extended from 18th July to 20th July.",
        "The Ministry of Education said that schools will re-open from next Thursday (21)."
